### 1. GET published events sorted by startDate
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event-service/Events?$filter=status eq 'Published'&$orderby=startDate asc

### 2. GET events filtered by type "Workshop"
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event-service/Events?$filter=eventType eq 'Workshop'

### 3. GET all registrations for a specific event
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event-service/Registrations?$filter=eventId eq ENTER_EVENT_UUID_HERE

### 4. POST a new registration
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event-service/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId": "ENTER_EVENT_UUID_HERE",
    "attendeeName": "Akhil Varma",
    "attendeeEmail": "akhil@example.com",
    "ticketType": "VIP",
    "amountPaid": 150.00
}

### 5. GET speakers sorted by rating descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event-service/Speakers?$orderby=rating desc

### 6. GET events with available seats
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event-service/Events?$filter=registeredCount lt maxAttendees

### 7. PATCH event status from "Draft" to "Published"
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event-service/Events(ID=ENTER_EVENT_UUID_HERE)
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Published"
}

### 8. POST feedback for an event
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event-service/Feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "eventId": "ENTER_EVENT_UUID_HERE",
    "attendeeEmail": "akhil@example.com",
    "overallRating": 5,
    "comment": "Excellent session on CAP modeling!"
}